<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٦٣٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3885">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ أَبِي الْأَسْوَدِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/820">أَبُو ضَمْرَةَ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدُ اللهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«اسْتَأْذَنَ الْعَبَّاسُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْمُطَّلِبِ <span class="special">﵁</span> رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> أَنْ يَبِيتَ بِمَكَّةَ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٥٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لَيَالِيَ مِنًى، مِنْ أَجْلِ سِقَايَتِهِ فَأَذِنَ لَهُ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>